rComments: Tim is the best professor. If you want to LEARN useful things, take his courses.

Tim is the bomb. Super smart, helpful, funny, and a cool guy. If you actually want to learn interesting stuff, take his classes. He has a lot of work study positions and ROPs available that give you valuable experience. He made me realize that physical geography is awesome, and he completely changed my life for the better.

Professor Duval is the most amazing professor ever. I have never learned so much from anyone before. He is super laid back and funny which makes his classes very entertaining. If you actually want to learn something or simply like beards, take his classes. The field experience is invaluable and he truly cares about his students.

Fantastic professor, one of my favourites. He was very helpful when you needed it and he was interesting to listen to during lectures. The textbook was not used much and when it was, the readings didnt really matter because he explained the concepts well. I would definitely recommend his class.

Probably the best prof I've ever had! Literally his class change my university experience. I'm not going to lie his class was hard, but I learned more in his class then any other course. He was very helpful and helped me be successful in all of my other classes:) Wish he taught more classes!
